{"memory_state":{"R":1,"S":10,"last_T_distance":"10day","D":5,"a":1},"current":"^cyanAI:OK！\n是求 ∫ y * ln(y) dy 吗？\n这题要用【分部积分法】哦！\n\n1. **设谁是u，谁是v**：\n令 u = ln(y)，dv = y dy\n那么 du = (1/y) dy，v = y²/2\n\n2. **套公式**：\n∫ u dv = uv - ∫ v du\n= (y²/2) * ln(y) - ∫ (y²/2) * (1/y) dy\n= (y²/2) * ln(y) - (1/2) * ∫ y dy\n\n3. **算出结果**：\n= (y²/2) * ln(y) - (1/2) * (y²/2) + C\n= **(y²/2) * ln(y) - y²/4 + C**\n\n也可以提出来写成：(y²/4) * (2ln(y) - 1) + C\n\n岛岛，别忘了最后那个常数 C 哦！","extraCurrent":{},"TIMESET":"20260302_165134"}
